rating_comment:
The flat has a kitchen and fridge, if you don't want to cook, there is a cafe below
where they serve burgers and good pizza.
The place is quite and Pranoy answer fast when we need something. I recommend it.

The hosts are very helpful and responsive.They reply very fast to all queries and are always available.They also do their best to make us comfortable be it by providing complimentary teabags,sugar&milk powder or being flexible with checkin/checkout timings.
The Nest Coffee Lounge is downstairs in same building so one can order breakfast/lunch/dinner from there as they prepare well at a reasonable charge. It is a college/student area, so you have many tea/snacks outlet nearby.
The place is a perfect example of "studio apartment"-very compact and well designed(around 250 Sq Ft).The tv has tata sky so one can use it in free time.
The only issue is mosquitoes which is a part of this location/surroundings so never open the windows/doors post evening as that is hazardous/painful which I realized after my 1st night because i had kept the windows and balcony door open for cool air!!
The place is around 20 kms from Bagdogra airport and clearly shows on map/Uber/Ola so no worries at all.
As I have not stayed full period you should try to refund back some portion of the amount as courtesy.

Have been there in kast week and it was a wonderful experience. The ambience is magnificent and peasant. If you are food lover, you should try their cuisines, available in the NEST Caffe owned by the same owner just beside the room. In case you need they deliver the food in your rooms.
Very nice experience, will surely visit again.

Pranoy’s place was perfect for my needs. Late arrival by air in Bagdogra and I only stayed one night. GREAT value, Pranoy was helpful in every possible way. I recommend this location to fellow travelers. Thank you Pranoy!
Fantastic spot to spend a night before going to Darjeeling/Gangtok. Host is very responsive on WhatsApp as well
I really liked the place , it was 10 mins walk to market area, quite place to enjoy the time, all facilities were superb, spacious ....Keep it Up, Wish I could stay for more

Value for money.
Helpful nature of host.
Privacy respected.
Great and quick communication.

Placed at a convinient location, about 10 mins from the main taxi stand. The host is always a call away, great communication. My only complaint would be with regards to cleanliness of the bathroom, rest was good!

Description is correct except you can not cook in the room. There s only a microwave and a kettle.
Excellent location.
Pranoy’s communication is excellent. Anything you need, you can just ask him. He really helped me out.

Host was very helpful, great communication and he was always available for help. Bed was comfy enough, rooms were very clean.
Also we got a chance to talk to hosts family members. They were all nice to us. Especially Aunt ji :)
Hope to book this room again on the way back to Kerala.
Good place. though the property is on the 2nd floor but the host helped us with our luggage when we checked in and while checking out they also helped with a local cab
It is very close to Venus more and Basu's cliniq. Transportation is easily available.
It was a nice place with all required amenities. Quiet and convenient location so could easily catch a connection for Darjeeling.
